'''RS-17''' was a rank in [[Republic Intelligence/Legends|Republic Intelligence]]. [[Phloremirlla Tenk]] held the rank after 23 [[Standard year/Legends|years]] of service, at which [[Time/Legends|time]] she was the intelligence chief for the minor [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Haruun Kal/Legends|Haruun Kal]].

